Document: AudioStreamSynchronized
Path: godot/classes/class_audiostreamsynchronized.rst
Summary: AudioStreamSynchronized class methods for managing synchronized audio streams and their volume levels.

- get_sync_stream(stream_index: int) → AudioStream (const): Retrieves the audio stream at the specified index.
- get_sync_stream_volume(stream_index: int) → float (const): Returns the volume level (in decibels) of the stream at the specified index.
- set_sync_stream(stream_index: int, audio_stream: AudioStream): Assigns a new audio stream to the specified index, replacing any existing stream.
- set_sync_stream_volume(stream_index: int, volume_db: float): Sets the volume level (in decibels) for the stream at the specified index.
