Document: AudioStreamSynchronized
Path: godot/classes/class_audiostreamsynchronized.rst
Summary: Configures the stream_count property for synchronizing multiple audio streams

stream_count (int): Set the total amount of streams that will be played back synchronized. Default: 0
- set_stream_count(value: int): Sets the number of synchronized streams
- get_stream_count() → int: Returns the current number of synchronized streams

Note: This property controls how many audio streams will be synchronized together. Increasing this value allows more streams to play in sync but may impact performance.
